{
  "stem": "12506.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything was done according to the law, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our town there was a-- a larger synagogue that we belonged to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was also Orthodox, but not as religious as ours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ours was more like a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And mostly, people, they had beard and payots and very religious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a  large synagogue in the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rabbi's name was Rosen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was-- he had a big yeshiva there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to come to study in our town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They even came from the United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember a few [NON-ENGLISH], the way we call them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were all Americans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they came there for a whole season.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then they went home and came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a very famous-- very famous yeshiva there in our town, yes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he was very dedicated to studying Bible and the Talmud and everything else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was a scholar in-- in this kind of studies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- he had managed a big yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were years that they had about more than 700 students there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to have their dormitories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they used to have their place where they used to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They got food there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the latest years they've built a new-- I would call it a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They got money from the United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was all brick, the way I remembered it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was the  most beautiful building in the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was a big yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Very famous.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, until I was nine I went to school in Sighet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when we moved away, when my father's father died, my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father went to what they called in Romania, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His mother lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
